The Crash Reel;;94;;96;;NC;;Snowboarder Kevin Pearce suffers a traumatic brain injury while training for the 2010 Winter Olympics. His family stands by his side as he struggles through rehab, but they object when he expresses his desire to return to his favorite sport.;;Documentary;;Lucy Walker;;2013;;Kevin Pearce,Shaun White,Mason Aguirre,Dr. Daniel Amen,Sarah Burke,Rory Bushfield;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_crash_reel_2013